クラス Constants

  • public final class Constants
extends Object
    Misc. constants used throughout JGit LFS extension.
    導入されたバージョン:
    4.3

    • フィールドのサマリー

      フィールド 
      修飾子とタイプ フィールドと説明
      static String CONTENT_TYPE_GIT_LFS_JSON
      Content type used by LFS REST API as defined in "https://github.com/github/git-lfs/blob/master/docs/api/v1/http-v1-batch.md"
      static String HDR_APPLICATION_OCTET_STREAM
      "arbitrary binary data" as defined in RFC 2046 "https://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2046.txt"
      static String LFS
      lfs folder
      static String LONG_HASH_FUNCTION
      Hash function used natively by Git LFS extension for large objects.
      static int LONG_OBJECT_ID_LENGTH
      A Git LFS large object hash is 256 bits, i.e. 32 bytes.
      static int LONG_OBJECT_ID_STRING_LENGTH
      A Git LFS large object can be expressed as a 64 character string of hexadecimal digits.

      • LONG_OBJECT_ID_LENGTH

        public static final int LONG_OBJECT_ID_LENGTH
        A Git LFS large object hash is 256 bits, i.e. 32 bytes.

        Changing this assumption is not going to be as easy as changing this declaration.

        関連項目:
        定数フィールド値

      • LONG_OBJECT_ID_STRING_LENGTH

        LONG_OBJECT_ID_LENGTH, 定数フィールド値

      • newMessageDigest

        public static MessageDigest newMessageDigest()
        Create a new digest function for objects.
        戻り値:
        a new digest object.
        例外:
        RuntimeException - this Java virtual machine does not support the required hash function. Very unlikely given that JGit uses a hash function that is in the Java reference specification.
